Package: geodiv
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Calculating Gradient Surface Metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Annie C. Smith
Maintainer: Annie C. Smith <coope378@msu.edu>
Description: Methods for calculating surface gradient metrics for
    continuous analysis of landscape features as found in McGarigal
    et al. (2009), Kedron et al. (2018), and Dahlin et al. (in 
    prep). Options for plotting are included.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 0.7.8),
    phonTools (>= 0.2-2.1),
    pracma (>= 2.2.2),
    raster (>= 2.8-4),
    spatial (>= 7.3-11),
    spatstat (>= 1.57-1),
    tibble (>= 1.4.2),
    e1071 (>= 1.7-0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat
